    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以 B 分出三条支路到 C、D、E。SDL 那个节点我标注为 SDL_GetError，文件和内存的命名也清楚了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
